OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FThe number of people living with HIV
OL,7,Fin Guernsey has risen by 14% in a year.
OL,9,FMore than 70 residents are now
OL,10,Faccessing specialist care for the
OL,11,Fcondition through the island's sexual
OL,12,Fhealth clinic, The Orchard Centre.
OL,14,FThe treatment bill is covered by the
OL,15,Fhealth service and expected to run
OL,16,Finto thousands of pounds per patient
OL,17,Fper year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
