CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FHowever, it is seen as a very cost-
OL,7,Feffective way to deal with HIV as it
OL,8,Fmaintains a person's health, reduces
OL,9,Fthe need for hospital admissions and
OL,10,Fprevents onward transmission.
OL,12,FEarly diagnosis can also
OL,13,Fsignificiantly bring down how
OL,14,Fexpensive treatment is and further
OL,15,Fhelp to reduce other people
OL,16,Fcontracting the condition.
OL,18,FIn parts of the UK, HIV testing is
OL,19,Fcarried out during routine hospital
OL,20,Fblood tests for people aged 16 and
OL,21,Fabove, unless they opt out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FGuernsey does not have a similar
OL,7,Fscreening programme due to budget
OL,8,Fconstraints, as it was expected to
OL,9,Fcost more than #100,000 a year.
OL,11,FLaura Brouard, Service Lead for the
OL,12,FOrchard Centre, explains: "We would
OL,13,Flove to follow what the UK guidance
OL,14,Fis, but obviously in a small
OL,15,Fjurisdiction we have competing demands
OL,16,Ffor funding."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
