PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FThe Orchard Centre does offer free and
OL,7,Fconfidential sexual health screening,
OL,8,Fincluding opt-out HIV tests, where
OL,9,Fmore than one in ten people choose not
OL,10,Fto be checked for the condition.
OL,12,FPeople in Guernsey living with HIV:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
