OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FExplaining the rise in HIV cases, the
OL,7,Fisland's Sexual and Reproductive
OL,8,FHealth Strategic Lead, Dr Jenny Rivers-
OL,9,FMoore, says: "Where you've got a small
OL,10,Fnumber of HIV cases, they translate
OL,11,Finto big percentages so where you
OL,12,Fmight have one, two or three new cases
OL,13,Fin a year it suddenly looks like a
OL,14,Fmassive change in the statistics."
OL,16,FWhat is HIV and how can it spread?
OL,18,FHIV or human immunodeficiency virus is
OL,19,Fspread through infected bodily fluids,
OL,20,Foften during unprotected sexual acts.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
