OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FIt can also transmit through shared
OL,7,Fsex toys, and needles or other
OL,8,Fequipment used for injecting drugs.
OL,10,FSomeone with the condition can give it
OL,11,Fto their baby during pregnancy or
OL,12,Fbirth.
OL,14,FWith effective treatment, the viral
OL,15,Fload can become undetectable - meaning
OL,16,Fit cannot be passed on to anyone else.
OL,18,FHIV cannot be spread through kissing,
OL,19,Fshaking hands or sharing food and
OL,20,Fdrinks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
