OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FMore details about causes, symptoms
OL,7,Fand treatment can be found on the NHS
OL,8,Fwebsite, with information on how to
OL,9,Fget tested for free in Guernsey
OL,10,Favailable on the States website.
OL,12,FEmma Cole was diagnosed with HIV in
OL,13,Fthe UK 35 years ago when her
OL,14,Fcontraception failed during sexual
OL,15,Fintercourse with her then partner, who
OL,16,Fhad not told her he had the condition.
OL,18,FShe founded the awareness group
OL,19,FPositive Voice and has spoken to
OL,20,Fstudents at more than 300 schools
OL,21,Fsince she was diagnosed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
