OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1784654323
OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,FEmma says: "If someone has been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed, they have access to
OL,8,Fmedications. They will live a long and
OL,9,Fhealthy life with HIV and if they're
OL,10,Fon treatment, they won't pass it on.
OL,12,F"Here in London, where I live, they
OL,13,Fhave opt-out testing now in Accident
OL,14,Fand Emergency Departments and that's
OL,15,Fbeen really effective at caputring
OL,16,Fthose people who would have never gone
OL,17,Fto a sexual health clinic or never
OL,18,Fconsidered themselves at risk of HIV.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
