OL,3,CGuernsey HIV cases rise by 14% in a
OL,4,Cyear
OL,6,F"Just under 2,000 people have been
OL,7,Fidentified as HIV positive who didn't
OL,8,Fknow."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/9
